pageContext.claim: “I have no doubt that, if the attack on Dr. Ford was as bad as she says, charges would have been immediately filed with local Law Enforcement Authorities by either her or her loving parents. I ask that she bring those filings forward so that we can learn  date, time, and place!”
pageContext.analysis: In the 1980s, when the alleged attack occurred, high school girls generally did not file a complaint -- and if they did, they were often not taken seriously.
